.org/wiki/Wycliffe%27s_Bible","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Wycliffe's Bible","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Lady Margery de Pyn was born in 1304, in Morwenstow, Cornwall, England, United Kingdom. She married John de Pyn Judge of Assize in 1326, in Upton Pyne, Devon, England. They were the parents of at least 3 sons. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1304–":"1304–Surnud","1302–1335":"1302–1335","1327–1363":"1327–1363","–Male":"Surnud","1304–Female":"1304–Surnud","1327":"1327","1304":"1304","1326":"1326","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1335":"1335","1302":"1302","1453":"1453","1363":"1363","1382":"1382","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Upton, Devon, England":"Upton, Devon, England","Ham, Morwenstow, Cornwall, England":"Morwenstow, Cornwall, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Upton Pyne, Devon, England":"Upton Pyne, Devon, England"},"fi":{"1304–":"1304–Kuollut","1302–1335":"1302–1335","1327–1363":"1327–1363","–Male":"Kuollut","1304–Female":"1304–Kuollut","1327":"1327","1304":"1304","1326":"1326","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1335":"1335","1302":"1302","1453":"1453","1363":"1363","1382":"1382","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Upton, Devon, England":"Upton, Devon, England","Ham, Morwenstow, Cornwall, England":"Morwenstow, Cornwall, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Upton Pyne, Devon, England":"Upton Pyne, Devon, England"},"fr":{"1304–":"1304–Décédée","1302–1335":"1302–1335","1327–1363":"1327–1363","–Male":"Décédé","1304–Female":"1304–Décédée","1327":"1327","1304":"1304","1326":"1326","1337":"1337","1315":"1315","1335":"1335","1302":"1302","1453":"1453","1363":"1363","1382":"1382","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","Upton, Devon, England":"Upton, Devon, Angleterre","Ham, Morwenstow, Cornwall, England":"Morwenstow, Cornouailles, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Upton Pyne, Devon, England":"Upton Pyne, Devon, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Lady Margery de Pyn est née en 1304, à Morwenstow, Cornouailles, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé John de Pyn Judge of Assize en 1326, à Upton Pyne, D